column4: I am wanting to order about 50 Kubuntu and 20 Xubuntu cd's thru shipit but I am was wanting them in time for Software freedom day. but shipit's says to allow up to 10 weeks by which time the days gone is there a way to get them quicker
the only thing i can think of is to fly into the netherlands and get them yourself
that's honestly the only suggestion i had.
